00:29:37,238 --> 00:29:38,876
- Field base, come in.
- All right.

400
00:29:38,958 --> 00:29:40,710
- Get you fixed up.
- Field base?

401
00:29:40,798 --> 00:29:42,948
Got something in your paw?

402
00:29:43,038 --> 00:29:45,347
This is Melbourne team calling.

403
00:29:45,438 --> 00:29:47,235
Field base, can we get a?

