Doc!

405
00:29:56,358 --> 00:29:57,632
Are you OK?

406
00:30:02,278 --> 00:30:04,189
I think I've broken my leg.

407
00:30:04,918 --> 00:30:07,830
All right. All right,
stay right there. I'll be right back!

408
00:30:10,638 --> 00:30:12,356
Whoa!

409
00:30:13,878 --> 00:30:16,711
Whoa! Wait, doc! Don't move!

410
00:30:16,798 --> 00:30:18,993
Doc! Doc!

411
00:30:22,238 --> 00:30:24,911
Doc! Hey! Don't tread water!

412
00:30:24,998 --> 00:30:26,147
Don't tread water!

413
00:30:27,878 --> 00:30:29,994
Look at me! You see the ice? Davis.

414
00:30:30,078 --> 00:30:31,989
Grab the ice!
Lt'll freeze you to it!

415
00:30:32,078 --> 00:30:34,831
It takes you a lot longer to freeze
than it does to drown!

416
00:30:39,598 --> 00:30:41,953
Good, good!
Davis, hang on! I'm coming down!

417
00:30:48,118 --> 00:30:50,188
All right, kids, come on!

418
00:30:55,238 --> 00:30:56,466
Hang on, doc!

419
00:31:04,438 --> 00:31:05,473
Maya, come here.

420
00:31:06,598 --> 00:31:08,793
I can't... I can't breathe.
I can't breathe.

421
00:31:08,878 --> 00:31:10,789
Take deep breaths, doc.

422
00:31:14,118 --> 00:31:15,756
Maya, take the rope.

423
00:31:16,798 --> 00:31:18,277
Go to doc.

424
00:31:18,358 --> 00:31:22,874
She's coming to you, doc.
She's coming to you.

425
00:31:22,958 --> 00:31:25,756
OK, Maya, down.

426
00:31:25,838 --> 00:31:27,237
Good girl. Crawl to the doc.

427
00:31:37,318 --> 00:31:39,593
Come on, Maya, I got you. It's OK.

428
00:31:39,678 --> 00:31:43,876
Come on, doc, stay in there with me.

429
00:31:44,558 --> 00:31:45,911
Come on, Maya.

430
00:31:46,958 --> 00:31:50,473
Easy, Maya. Easy.

431
00:31:52,678 --> 00:31:54,509
Good girl.

432
00:32:04,478 --> 00:32:07,231
Good job, Maya.
Put the line over him.

433
00:32:07,318 --> 00:32:09,673
Good girl. Doc.

