00:32:14,278 --> 00:32:17,031
You gotta get your elbow
and your arm up through the loop.

437
00:32:17,118 --> 00:32:19,916
You can do it. There you go.

438
00:32:20,798 --> 00:32:24,586
Good job, doc. Yeah, just like that.

439
00:32:24,678 --> 00:32:27,511
All right. Maya, come on.

440
00:32:30,278 --> 00:32:32,951
Good girl, Maya. Good girl.

441
00:32:33,038 --> 00:32:36,667
I got you, doc. I got you.

442
00:32:36,758 --> 00:32:38,316
Keep it tight.

443
00:32:38,958 --> 00:32:40,152
Line 'em up, Maya!

444
00:32:42,558 --> 00:32:45,868
Right now! Right now!
Come on! Take it home!

445
00:32:49,878 --> 00:32:51,357
Line up! Hike!

446
00:32:51,438 --> 00:32:54,236
Come on, Maya!
Come on, Old Jack!

447
00:32:54,878 --> 00:32:56,470
Come on, kids!

448
00:33:00,318 --> 00:33:01,546
Hike!

449
00:33:05,878 --> 00:33:09,473
All right, doc, you hang in there, OK?

450
00:33:09,558 --> 00:33:11,514
We're gonna get you home.
All right?

451
00:33:11,598 --> 00:33:13,156
Don't you worry.

452
00:33:13,638 --> 00:33:16,436
- I'm gonna get you back.
- I'm sorry.

453
00:33:16,518 --> 00:33:18,793
You're gonna get home
and see your family, doc.

454
00:33:18,878 --> 00:33:21,267
You're gonna see your son, all right?

455
00:33:38,758 --> 00:33:40,396
Come here, Maya.

456
00:33:40,478 --> 00:33:43,390
Maya, you got to get us home!
Get us home!

457
00:33:49,318 --> 00:33:51,957
Go get up there, Max! Maya needs you!

458
00:33:54,558 --> 00:33:58,471
Right now! Right now! Hike! Hike!

459
00:34:18,078 --> 00:34:20,956
I can fly in this, Andy. You know I can.

