475
00:37:03,038 --> 00:37:04,915
- Get the stretcher now!
- Got it!

476
00:37:06,398 --> 00:37:08,468
- I don't like that cough.
- Get the dogs.

477
00:37:08,558 --> 00:37:10,833
Look at those hands! Get him in!

478
00:37:10,918 --> 00:37:12,829
- Come on, Jerry.
- Let's go!

479
00:37:12,918 --> 00:37:16,672
Good team. Good team.

480
00:37:17,998 --> 00:37:19,750
Good girl, Maya!

481
00:37:19,838 --> 00:37:21,191
You got us home.

482
00:37:25,838 --> 00:37:27,829
All right,
let's have a look at this leg.

